---
// @ts-ignore
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="SAVOY Beach Hotel & Thermal Spa" description="Eine Oase des Luxus und Wohlbefindens. Ganzjährig geöffnet in Bibione." lang="de" currentPath="/">

    <section class="relative h-screen flex flex-col justify-center items-center overflow-hidden text-center px-4">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1540541338287-41700207dee6?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2000&q=80" alt="Savoy Dark" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 scale-105 pointer-events-none" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-black/20 to-[#050505]"></div>
        
        <div class="relative z-10 mt-16">
            <h1 class="text-7xl md:text-9xl text-white font-light tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 drop-shadow-2xl" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                Savoy
            </h1>
            <p class="text-white/90 text-sm md:text-xl tracking-[0.4em] uppercase font-light" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                Beach Hotel & Thermal Spa
            </p>
            <div class="w-px h-24 bg-white/30 mx-auto mt-12"></div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative py-32 px-6 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-20">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="sticky top-32 h-[70vh] overflow-hidden">
                <img loading="lazy" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1611892440504-42a792e24d32?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Dienstleistungen" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-1000 pointer-events-none">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center pt-20 md:pt-0">
            <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">01. Exzellenz</p>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white font-light leading-none mb-12" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                Maßgeschneiderte <br> <i>Services</i>.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-8 text-sm md:text-lg lg:text-xl font-light text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-lg" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                <p>Ein Universum von Aufmerksamkeiten, exklusiv für Sie entworfen. Vom Privatstrand bis zu unserem digitalen Concierge ist jedes Detail darauf abgestimmt, Ihnen einen unvergleichlichen Aufenthalt zu bieten.</p>
                <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
                    <a href="/de/servizi" class="text-white text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase flex items-center gap-4 hover:gap-8 transition-all">
                        Aufmerksamkeiten entdecken <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-white block"></span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative py-32 px-6 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-20">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden h-[60vh] md:h-[80vh]">
                <img loading="lazy" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544161515-4ab6ce6db874?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Thermal Spa" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-1000 pointer-events-none">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">02. Wohlbefinden</p>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white font-light leading-none mb-12" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                <i>Heilende</i> <br> Gewässer.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-8 text-sm md:text-lg lg:text-xl font-light text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-lg" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                <p>Ein geheimer Korridor trennt Sie von der Welt. Im Bademantel erreichen Sie von Ihrer Suite aus direkt und in völliger Privatsphäre die Quellen der Bibione Thermae.</p>
                <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
                    <a href="/de/spa" class="text-white text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase flex items-center gap-4 hover:gap-8 transition-all">
                        Behandlungen entdecken <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-white block"></span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative py-32 px-6 max-w-screen-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-20 border-b border-white/10">
        <div class="md:w-1/2">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden h-[60vh] md:h-[80vh]">
                <img loading="lazy" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514362545857-3bc16c4c7d1b?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1200&q=80" alt="Restaurant" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition duration-1000 pointer-events-none">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:w-1/2 flex flex-col justify-center">
            <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">03. Geschmack</p>
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl text-white font-light leading-none mb-12" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                <i>Sinnliche</i> <br> Reise.
            </h2>
            <div class="space-y-8 text-sm md:text-lg lg:text-xl font-light text-gray-400 leading-relaxed max-w-lg" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
                <p>Vom Fine Dining im Duca d'Aosta bis zur Intimität unseres In-Suite Dinings. Ein Mosaik aus Aromen, Atmosphären und Exzellenz, das jeden Ihrer Wünsche erfüllt.</p>
                <div class="pt-8 border-t border-gray-800">
                    <a href="/de/ristorante" class="text-white text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase flex items-center gap-4 active:gap-8 md:hover:gap-8 transition-all">
                        Erlebnisse entdecken <span class="w-12 h-[1px] bg-white block"></span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-24">
            <p class="text-[#d4af37] text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">Verwöhnen Sie sich</p>
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl text-white font-light" style="font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;">
                <i>Exklusive</i> Aufmerksamkeiten.
            </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-y-16 gap-x-8 text-center" style="font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;">
            
            <a href="/de/servizi" class="group block cursor-pointer">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 mx-auto mb-6 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-[#d4af37] group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="5" stroke-width="1"/><path stroke-width="1" d="M12 1v2m0 18v2M4.22 4.22l1.42 1.42m12.72 12.72l1.42 1.42M1 12h2m18 0h2M4.22 19.78l1.42-1.42M18.36 5.64l1.42-1.42"/>
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] md:text-[13px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2 transition-colors group-hover:text-[#d4af37]">Privatstrand</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">VIP-Bereich</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/de/spa" class="group block cursor-pointer">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 mx-auto mb-6 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-[#d4af37] group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 2.69l5.66 5.66a8 8 0 11-11.31 0z"/>
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] md:text-[13px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2 transition-colors group-hover:text-[#d4af37]">Thermal-Tunnel</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Direkter Zugang</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/de/servizi" class="group block cursor-pointer">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 mx-auto mb-6 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-[#d4af37] group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <rect x="3" y="8" width="18" height="4" rx="1" stroke-width="1"/><path stroke-width="1" d="M4 8l2-4h12l2 4M4 12v6a1 1 0 001 1h14a1 1 0 001-1v-6M7 16h.01M17 16h.01"/>
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] md:text-[13px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2 transition-colors group-hover:text-[#d4af37]">Überdachte Garage</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">E-Ladestationen</p>
            </a>

            <a href="/de/servizi" class="group block cursor-pointer">
                <svg class="w-10 h-10 md:w-12 md:h-12 mx-auto mb-6 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-[#d4af37] group-hover:scale-110 transition-all duration-500" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <circle cx="5.5" cy="17.5" r="3.5"/>
                    <circle cx="18.5" cy="17.5" r="3.5"/>
                    <path d="M15 6a1 1 0 1 0 0-2 1 1 0 0 0 0 2zm-3 11.5V14l-3-3 4-3 2 3h2"/>
                </svg>
                <h3 class="text-white text-[11px] md:text-[13px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2 transition-colors group-hover:text-[#d4af37]">Fahrradverleih</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-500 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider">Bibione erkunden</p>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

</BaseLayout>